Play根据伊朗卫生部最新消息，截至3月16日中午，伊朗累计确诊新冠肺炎病例14991例，其中4996例康复，853例死亡。
Up to noon March 16, Iran had confirmed a cumulative total of 14,991 new cases of pneumonia, including 4,996 cases of convalescence and 853 deaths, according to an update from Iran's Ministry of Health.
为遏制疫情发展，尽早发现疑似感染的病例，伊朗本月初宣布启动国家动员计划，将陆续向全国各地派出30万个医疗小组逐户排查疫情。
Earlier this month, Iran announced a national mobilization plan to send 300,000 medical teams around the country to conduct house-to-house surveillance of the disease in an effort to halt the spread of the epidemic and detect suspected cases as soon as possible.
据伊朗伊斯兰共和国通讯社报道，伊朗卫生部副部长阿里雷扎·雷西3月15日表示，截至当天伊朗启动的国家动员计划完成了1000万人的疫情排查工作。
Iran's health minister, Ali Reza Rasi, said on March 15 that Iran's national mobilization plan, which began on the same day, had cleared 10 million people of the disease, the IRNA reported.
排查后，发现有21万人出现了至少一种疑似症状。
As a result of the screening, at least 210,000 people were found to have at least one suspected symptom.
当地时间3月10日至15日，凤凰卫视驻伊朗记者李睿走上德黑兰街头，询问当地人对疫情的看法。
From 10 to 15 March local time, the Iranian correspondent for Phoenix TV, Li Rui, took to the streets of Tehran to ask local people about the outbreak.
